. Petronilla Paveley, was 30. He married Mrs. Sarah De Paveley about 1240, in Paulerspury, Northamptonshire, England. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1288, in Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 69."},"et":{"about 1220–1288":"umbes 1220–1288","1220–1288":"1220–1288","1231–1299":"1231–1299","1245–1329":"1245–1329","1199–1250":"1199–1250","1192–1245":"1192–1245","1231":"1231","1220":"1220","1250":"1250","1192":"1192","1259":"1259","1224":"1224","1245":"1245","1288":"1288","1299":"1299","1199":"1199","about 1245":"umbes 1245","about 1220":"umbes 1220","about 1240":"umbes 1240","1329":"1329","Paulersbury, Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"England","Paulerspury, Northamptonshire, England":"Paulerspury, Northamptonshire, England"},"fi":{"about 1220–1288":"noin 1220–1288","1220–1288":"1220–1288","1231–1299":"1231–1299","1245–1329":"1245–1329","1199–1250":"1199–1250","1192–1245":"1192–1245","1231":"1231","1220":"1220","1250":"1250","1192":"1192","1259":"1259","1224":"1224","1245":"1245","1288":"1288","1299":"1299","1199":"1199","about 1245":"noin 1245","about 1220":"noin 1220","about 1240":"noin 1240","1329":"1329","Paulersbury, Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"England","Paulerspury, Northamptonshire, England":"Paulerspury, Northamptonshire, England"},"fr":{"about 1220–1288":"environ 1220–1288","1220–1288":"1220–1288","1231–1299":"1231–1299","1245–1329":"1245–1329","1199–1250":"1199–1250","1192–1245":"1192–1245","1231":"1231","1220":"1220","1250":"1250","1192":"1192","1259":"1259","1224":"1224","1245":"1245","1288":"1288","1299":"1299","1199":"1199","about 1245":"environ 1245","about 1220":"environ 1220","about 1240":"environ 1240","1329":"1329","Paulersbury, Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","England":"Angleterre","Paulerspury, Northamptonshire, England":"Paulerspury, Northamptonshire, An